CIHM-Meta

This is a module used by Canadiana to impliment the metadata bus.

Tools:

* hammer - reads METS data from the repository and generates a JSON file
           stored in the 'internalmeta' couchdb database
* solrstream - Streams updates in 'cosearch' CouchDB database to Solr.
* reposync - Keeps 'internalmeta' and 'wipmeta' CouchDB databases current
             about the public availability of replicas of AIP content
             in repositories.
* press  - Checks for 'internalmeta' updates and pushes updates to
           'cosearch' and 'copresentation' databases.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

We run this module from a Docker image built with
https://github.com/c7a/cihm-metadatabus

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

  https://github.com/c7a/CIHM-Meta has an issue tracker which should be
  used for any questions.

  https://github.com/c7a/CIHM-Meta/blob/master/HISTORY.md contains
  a note about the history of this module.


